  "detailed_review": "<p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What do you like best about Synup?</strong></p><p id=\"\">I love the outstanding work. I love that they really help they clients but i love the the product that they deliever . awsome!!!!!</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What do you dislike about Synup?</strong></p><p id=\"\">Its nothing i do not dislike about they. They get the job done just like they say they would.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What problems is Synup solving and how is that benefiting you?</strong></p><p id=\"\">They help me get my business all over the internet. When having a business you must be findable. They help my company get on yahoo google ect they really the best and i thank them for all they done for me.</p>",
